{"tid":2221602,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇兄弟去過納卡 (納哥諾-卡拉巴克)？","createTime":"2020-09-28T13:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T18:48:19.000Z","uid":73381,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5e1e2398882dc32a9b2e9c8f99fabe43cd999e","tid":2221602,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"由亞美尼亞首都Yerevan搭巴士去納卡首都Stepanakert，大約五至六個鐘就到，大部分都係山路，搭到有啲想嘔。<br />\n<br />\n落左車會發現同亞美尼亞比完全係兩個世界，Stepanakert勁細，基本上二十分鐘可以行哂，去到第一件事就係去申請簽證，填張表再課金就搞掂。市內其實冇咩野睇，都係博物館嗰啲。<br />\n<br />\n係路上行基本上每個人都會同你打招呼，可能佢地少見亞洲人，但完全溝通唔到，基本上冇人識英文，同佢地講米希達恩佢地會好大反應同好開心，條撚樣係當地勁受歡迎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個國家基本上啲樓都溶溶爛爛，好多廢棄嘅舊屋同舊大樓，大部分人都好撚窮，去到納卡完全唔似係去緊旅行，成個感覺就係去咗個戰後嘅地方咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgOmUzW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgOmUzW.jpg&h=a1fd9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYzQNUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYzQNUf.jpg&h=dbe8d555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfMWJsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfMWJsG.jpg&h=97b3c69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieXSgNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FieXSgNM.jpg&h=28312a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPCOzzw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPCOzzw.jpg&h=c38e5e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1EpSmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1EpSmg.jpg&h=8bf2b248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7VXsUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7VXsUJ.jpg&h=608ccc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3vc1eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3vc1eP.jpg&h=272ef323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77814421ddf8b2b2eeace3a2e5f0e98b42085f96","tid":2221602,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"樓主祖先屠殺過亞美尼亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791b73ecc3a5957d42f1e9ae4bb75f2e848004b7","tid":2221602,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"米青達恩都撚樣？<br />\n你無撚野下話？<br />\n利申：有少少亞美利堅血統"},{"pid":"58c28cf2b572cc35987a9b67bd20339b085739c9","tid":2221602,"uid":367051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"b120877068f9fee6c0344c30cf10f4c940dbbb89","tid":2221602,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77814421ddf8b2b2eeace3a2e5f0e98b42085f96","tid":2221602,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"樓主祖先屠殺過亞美尼亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"佢隻突厥狗WWI殺左200m亞美人"},{"pid":"34e84ad078e446de8aaca62161d71cefa96f15b4","tid":2221602,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77814421ddf8b2b2eeace3a2e5f0e98b42085f96","tid":2221602,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"樓主祖先屠殺過亞美尼亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:16:41.000Z","msg":"我揸BNO當地班撚樣唔知我身份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459f2572617c01ed25838d68e4108e532fea5822","tid":2221602,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b120877068f9fee6c0344c30cf10f4c940dbbb89","tid":2221602,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77814421ddf8b2b2eeace3a2e5f0e98b42085f96","tid":2221602,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime